Upgrade procedure for sendmail

Source: https://ftp.sendmail.org/pub/sendmail/sendmail.VERSION.tar.gz

To upgrade to a new version:

1. Download and extract the new tarball to /tmp/sendmail/sendmail-VERSION
2. Use the vendor-update skill (vendor/sendmail/dist, contrib/sendmail)
3. Rename sendmail/ to src/ before syncing into the worktree
4. Resolve modify/delete conflicts by keeping master deletions (git rm)

